<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**ESP-IDF**<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>Download<sp/>and<sp/>install<sp/>the<sp/>ESP-IDF<sp/>from<sp/>[https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/get-started/](https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/get-started/).</highlight></codeline>
