<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>**VS<sp/>Code<sp/>Extensions**<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>Install<sp/>the<sp/>following<sp/>in<sp/>VS<sp/>Code:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**ESP-IDF**<sp/>(by<sp/>Espressif)</highlight></codeline>
